reviews.text: Proud to support Mosaic Multicultural Connections for their continuous efforts in empowering multicultural communities and promoting understanding and collaboration. Your work makes a real difference and truly deserves appreciation.
Mosaic Services is a great organisation, and Elena is incredibly helpful and knowledgeable. Highly recommend!

Mosaic is really good. Thy till us every thing we need, and if there are any cores my casa manger send it to me That is in top of the Arabic women speaking group that have all the information we need and always send us updates.

Mosaic Multicultural Connections is an amazing organisation! They always provide excellent support and care for our community. I’m truly grateful for their kindness, professionalism, and dedication. Thank you so much to the whole Mosaic team for everything you do!

Its very helpful group that they are helping women and child in Newcastle. I really appreciate Miza and Claria who been help me during my unplanned pregnancy time. I was very stressed and depressed. No income and large amounts of bill make me felt sickness. I couldn’t sleep night by night . They help me with their warm hearts and make me feel the beauty of life. I will remember these and hope that one day I can help others like them.
A group of people helping other people to get them a better life. I really like the way they interact with you. They are always so smiley .
Wonderful community support and friendly staff. They do amazing work for the Newcastle area.
Great resources for new families and migrants. Very welcoming environment.
